<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 03:12:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国科技股反弹提振亚洲股市，就业成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-02/</link><description>由于 Meta 和亚马逊的业绩超出预期，周五美国科技股尾盘反弹提振亚洲股市，而投资者正在为美国就业数据做好准备，如果数据低于预期，可能会加速降息的押注。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 02:05:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>日本向唐纳德·特朗普传达的信息：不要与中国达成协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-message-donald-trump-dont-cut-deal-with-china-2024-02-02/</link><description>日本一直试图向美国总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普传达一个信息：不要试图与中国达成任何可能颠覆多年来遏制北京的集体努力的协议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 01:04:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-message-donald-trump-dont-cut-deal-with-china-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>美元本周将下跌；接下来美国就业数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-poised-weekly-decline-us-jobs-data-up-next-2024-02-02/</link><description>华尔街大型科技公司财报乐观后，周五美元普遍下跌，风险情绪积极，交易员等待当天晚些时候公布的美国就业数据，以判断美联储多久可以开始降息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 01:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-poised-weekly-decline-us-jobs-data-up-next-2024-02-02/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国销售滞后，苹果 iPhone 目标比华尔街目标低数十亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-quarterly-profit-revenue-top-wall-street-targets-china-lags-2024-02-01/</link><description>苹果公司周四预测，由于中国业务受到打击，iPhone 销量将下降，总收入目标将低于华尔街预期 60 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 21:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-quarterly-profit-revenue-top-wall-street-targets-china-lags-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>因担心中国而导致预算超支30%后，印度将继续在边境公路上投入资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-keep-spending-border-roads-after-30-budget-overrun-china-fears-2024-02-01/</link><description>印度政府周四表示，由于这两个拥核邻国之间的紧张关系，印度政府将继续增加资金用于修建靠近中国边境的公路，本财年的公路建设支出比计划多出 30%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 12:46:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-keep-spending-border-roads-after-30-budget-overrun-china-fears-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大鹅依靠中国奢侈品需求复苏预测季度强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/canada-goose-misses-quarterly-revenue-expectations-2024-02-01/</link><description>加拿大鹅控股公司 (Canada Goose Holdings) 周四预测第四季度收入高于分析师预期，这家奢侈品制造商押注中国这一重要市场的大幅反弹，将有助于渡过美国经济放缓的难关</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 11:55:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/canada-goose-misses-quarterly-revenue-expectations-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国要求乌克兰将其公司从“战争赞助者”名单中删除</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-warns-ukraine-over-naming-its-firms-sponsors-war-sources-2024-02-01/</link><description>中国周四要求乌克兰立即将十几家中国公司从被指定为“国际战争赞助者”的公司名单中删除，并表示希望基辅“消除负面影响”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 11:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-warns-ukraine-over-naming-its-firms-sponsors-war-sources-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>旅游业复苏，香港 12 月零售额增长 7.8%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-dec-retail-sales-up-78-tourism-recovers-2024-02-01/</link><description>周四官方数据显示，由于旅游业持续改善，香港 12 月份零售额连续 13 个月增长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 09:42:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-dec-retail-sales-up-78-tourism-recovers-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>台湾选出议会议长执政党观点亲中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-elects-parliament-speaker-ruling-party-views-pro-china-2024-02-01/</link><description>台湾议会周四选举最大反对党的前总统候选人为新议长，他将负责接待来访的外国议员，执政党称他是亲中国的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:26:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-elects-parliament-speaker-ruling-party-views-pro-china-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：英伟达面向中国的新型人工智能芯片将以与华为产品相似的价格出售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidias-new-china-focused-ai-chip-set-be-sold-similar-price-huawei-product-2024-02-01/</link><description>知情人士称，英伟达已开始接受经销商预订一款新的中国专用人工智能芯片，这些芯片的定价与华为的竞争对手产品相当。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 07:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidias-new-china-focused-ai-chip-set-be-sold-similar-price-huawei-product-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国称越南稀土产量随中国经济增长而下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/vietnam-rare-earths-output-drops-chinas-grows-us-says-2024-02-01/</link><description>根据一份年度报告，美国地质机构大幅下调了对越南稀土产量的预估，并预计尽管越南资源基础丰富，但产量仍将进一步下降，该报告显示，主要生产国中国的产量有所增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 06:54:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/vietnam-rare-earths-output-drops-chinas-grows-us-says-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾计划购买潜艇以捍卫南海主权——高级官员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-plans-buy-submarines-defend-sovereignty-south-china-sea-senior-2024-02-01/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯已批准军队现代化的第三阶段，其中包括购买该国第一艘潜艇，以捍卫其在有争议的南中国海的海洋主权。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 06:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-plans-buy-submarines-defend-sovereignty-south-china-sea-senior-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车将停止资助 Polestar，可能将股份转让给吉利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automaker-volvo-cars-stop-funding-polestar-quarterly-earnings-above-estimates-2024-02-01/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车周四表示，将停止向北极星汽车控股公司提供资金，并将这个陷入困境的豪华汽车品牌的责任移交给沃尔沃最大股东中国吉利控股公司。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 06:09:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automaker-volvo-cars-stop-funding-polestar-quarterly-earnings-above-estimates-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>人权观察就中国强迫劳工风险向汽车制造商发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/human-rights-watch-warns-carmakers-over-china-forced-labour-risk-2024-02-01/</link><description>人权观察敦促特斯拉、大众和比亚迪等汽车制造商采取更多措施，确保可能使用维吾尔族强迫劳动制造的材料不会进入其供应链。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 05:09:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/human-rights-watch-warns-carmakers-over-china-forced-labour-risk-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院以2019年冲击立法会后骚乱罪判处四人有罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-convicts-four-rioting-after-2019-legislature-storming-2024-02-01/</link><description>周四，香港一家法院认定四人犯有 2019 年民主抗议活动期间冲击金融中心立法机关后发生的骚乱罪，另外八人也承认了对该事件的指控。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 03:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-convicts-four-rioting-after-2019-legislature-storming-2024-02-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>